kpi.name: M386B2C17

kpi_info.title: The average time of the durations of the internal released connections
kpi_info.use: The average time of the durations of the internal released connections during the period. Clear code range for internal failure released connection: 400...7FF. The unit of time in ASCII report is seconds, and in XML reports, it is 10 milliseconds.

kpi.kpi_alias: The average time of the durations of the internal released connections
